OL,4,CBradford fire tweets
OL,6,FA Doncaster Rovers fan has been banned
OL,7,Ffrom the club for life over "hateful"
OL,8,Fsocial media posts about the Bradford
OL,9,FCity fire disaster.
OL,11,FThe club said it received multiple
OL,12,Fcomplaints from members of the public
OL,13,F"understandably distressed" over the
OL,14,Fcomments.
OL,16,FFifty-six people died and more than
OL,17,F250 were injured when Bradford city's
OL,18,Fstadium caught fire in May 1985.
