OL,6,FIt follows a lifetime ban for a
OL,7,FSheffield Wednesday fan, who has also
OL,8,Fbeen sacked from his job and charged
OL,9,Fby police, over an "abhorrent" social
OL,10,Fmedia post about the death of a rival
OL,11,Fsupporter.
OL,13,FThe club took action after a post on X
OL,14,Fappearing to mock the death of West
OL,15,FBrom fan Mark Townsend.
